title: Ahmad Al Shoura - Mohammad - A rational analysis (Arabic)
description:
<a href="http://www.alshoura.org." rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.alshoura.org.</a> An Ahmad Al Shoura show. This episode of the "Fettallaga" series is episode 6, entitled "Mohammad - A rational analysis".

Language: Arabic.
Duration: 0:54:54.

Who was Mohammad? Was he a lier, a devil possessed, a social reformer or a seeker of fortune and authority? Was he misguided, or is it true that he was a Messenger of the Creator of the universe?
